eld in the compact with a very strong magnet.</li>\n  <li>This is our first step to reducing the amount of single use primary bottles, in a long journey.</li>\n</ul>"},{"key":"100% Vegan","heading":"100% Vegan and Cruelty Free","subheading":"Products that are good for your skin, your thoughts, and the planet.","content":"<ul>\n  <li>German Chamomile Flower Extract calms and soothes sensitive skin.</li>\n  <li>Sunflower Seed Oil has rich antioxidant and anti-inflammatory properties hat soothe sensitive skin and redness.</li>\n  <li>Cacao Seed Butter is high in fatty acids providing hydration and nourishment to the skin, to improve elasticity. The fat in cocoa butter forms a protective barrier over skin to hold in moisture.</li>\n  <li>Jojoba Oil regulates sebum production with the most similar molecular structure to the skin. Soothing and moisturising, it is noncomedogenic, meaning it won’t clog pores.</li>\n  <li>Full Ingredient List - Bronzing Powder #1 Mica - Mineral Origin (Sustainably Sourced), Aluminium Starch Octenylsuccinate - Vegetal Origin, Squalane - Plant Origin, Zinc Stearate - Vegetal Origin, Magnesium Carbonate - Mineral Origin, Lauroyl lysine - Plant Origin, Glyceryl Caprylate - Vegetal Origin, P-Anisic Acid - Antiseptic Preservative, Chlorphenesin - Antifungal & Antibacterial Preservative, Chamomilla recutita (matricaria) flower extract - Plant Origin,, Helianthus Annuus (sunflower) seed oil - Plant Origin, Tourmaline - Mineral Origin, Tocopherol, Retinyl Palimate - Vegetal (Coconut) Origin, Calcium Sulfate - Mineral Origin, Manganese Sulfate -, Mineral Origin, Propylene Glycol, May Contain +/- Iron Oxides - CI 77491 - Mineral Origin, Iron Oxide - CI 77491 - Mineral Origin, Iron Oxide - CI 77499 - Mineral Origin</li>\n  <li>Bronzing Powder #2 & #3 Mica - Mineral Origin (Sustainably Sourced), Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Wax, Squalane - Plant Origin, Zea Mays (Corn) Starch, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Glyceryl Caprylate, Citrus Paradisi (Grapefruit) Seed Oil, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Glyceryl Undecylenate, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), CI 77499 (Iron Oxides), CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide)</li>\n  <li>Bronzing Powder #4 Mica - Mineral Origin (Sustainably Sourced), Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Wax, Squalane - Plant Origin, Zea Mays (Corn) Starch, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Glyceryl Caprylate, Citrus Paradisi (Grapefruit) Seed Oil, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Glyceryl Undecylenate, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), CI 77492 (Iron Oxides), CI 77499 (Iron Oxides), CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide), CI 15850 (Red 6), CI 19140 (Yellow 5 Lake), CI 73360 (Red 30 Lake)</li>\n  <li>Lip Oil Clear: Ricinus communis (Castor) seed oil, Prunus amygdalus dulcis (Sweet almond) oil, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Butyrospermum parkii (Shea) butter, Euphorbia cerifera (Candelillia) wax, Mica (Sustainably Sourced), Copernicia cerifera (Carnauba) wax, Argania Spinosa (Argan) kernal oil, Simmondsia chinensis (Jojoba) seed oil, Squalane (Olive Oil) Glycine soja (Soybean) oil, Tocopherol Acetate (Vitamin E), Aloe barbadensis (Aloe Vera) leaf extract, Citric Acid, CI 77891 Tint Additions: (Titanium Dioxide) CI 77491, 77492, 77499 (Iron Oxides).</li>\n  <li>Kabuki Brush - Synthetic Fibers, retractable cover and protective lid.</li>\n</ul>"},{"key":"42 Day Returns","heading":"42 Day Return","subheading":"Our 42 Day Return Policy","content":"<ul>\n  <li>You can return your item within 42 days of receiving it, after chatting with our team, for a full refund or an exchange</li>\n  <li>We do this because we believe in and stand by our product, and you’ll have to have a pretty good reason for wanting to return it, and we’d like to honour that.</li>\n  <li>Why 42 days? Why not? Email <a href=\"mailto:bunnies@itsallfluff.com\" class=\"underline\">bunnies@itsallfluff.com</a> to tell us how you feel.</li>\n  <li>Be gentle, Fluff has feelings too.</li>\n</ul>"},{"key":"Free shipping over $50","heading":"Free Shipping","subheading":"Free Shipping over $50 in Aus","content":"<ul>\n  <li>Fluff ships products every Wednesday & Friday.</li>\n  <li>Free shipping for orders over $50 AUD </li>\n  <li>Otherwise it's $10 AUD. Delivered by Australia Post in about about a week.</li>\n  <li>Express Shipping: It’s not free, but it is quick. About 1-2 days quick. And about $15 exactly.</li>\n  <li>Standard International: It’s $25, we can’t afford free yet. And takes around 7 - 14 working days.</li>\n  <li>(All timelines are subject to world pandemics) </li>\n</ul>"}],"upsells":[{"category":"Refills","handles":["bronzing-powder-refill","lip-oil-refill"],"heading":"Shop Refills","type":"Product"},{"category":"All","handles":["face-oil-1","face-oil-2","face-oil-3","cleanser"],"heading":"Best Sellers","type":"Product"}],"sections":[{"type":"swipeImage","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.471264367816092,"src":"/static/3040956bb5ea2f18d831cfa187cec387/26852/pdp-cloud-collection-how-to.jpg","srcSet":"/static/3040956bb5ea2f18d831cfa187cec387/d64b1/pdp-cloud-collection-how-to.jpg 256w,\n/static/3040956bb5ea2f18d831cfa187cec387/89b9c/pdp-cloud-collection-how-to.jpg 512w,\n/static/3040956bb5ea2f18d831cfa187cec387/26852/pdp-cloud-collection-how-to.jpg 1024w,\n/static/3040956bb5ea2f18d831cfa187cec387/4d6da/pdp-cloud-collection-how-to.jpg 1344w","srcWebp":"/static/3040956bb5ea2f18d831cfa187cec387/e0f73/pdp-cloud-collection-how-to.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/3040956bb5ea2f18d831cfa187cec387/b42dd/pdp-cloud-collection-how-to.webp 256w,\n/static/3040956bb5ea2f18d831cfa187cec387/e4e36/pdp-cloud-collection-how-to.webp 512w,\n/static/3040956bb5ea2f18d831cfa187cec387/e0f73/pdp-cloud-collection-how-to.webp 1024w,\n/static/3040956bb5ea2f18d831cfa187cec387/9b8f4/pdp-cloud-collection-how-to.webp 1344w","sizes":"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"}},"publicURL":"/static/3040956bb5ea2f18d831cfa187cec38