 has antimicrobial properties to soothe skin that is prone to irritations.</li>\n  <li>Full Ingredient List - Cannabis Sativa (Hemp) Seed Oil, Bakuchiol, Boswellia Carterii (Frankincense) Gum Oil, Achillea Millefolium (Yarrow) Oil, Tocopherol.</li>\n</ul>"},{"key":"42 Day Returns","heading":"42 Day Return","subheading":"Our 42 Day Return Policy","content":"<ul>\n  <li>You can return your item within 42 days of receiving it, after chatting with our team, for a full refund or an exchange</li>\n  <li>We do this because we believe in and stand by our product, and you’ll have to have a pretty good reason for wanting to return it, and we’d like to honour that.</li>\n  <li>Why 42 days? Why not? Email <a href=\"mailto:bunnies@itsallfluff.com\" class=\"underline\">bunnies@itsallfluff.com</a> to tell us how you feel.</li>\n  <li>Be gentle, Fluff has feelings too.</li>\n</ul>"},{"key":"Free shipping over $50","heading":"Free Shipping","subheading":"Free Shipping over $50 in Aus","content":"<ul>\n  <li>Fluff ships products every Wednesday & Friday.</li>\n  <li>Free shipping for orders over $50 AUD </li>\n  <li>Otherwise it's $10 AUD. Delivered by Australia Post in about about a week.</li>\n  <li>Express Shipping: It’s not free, but it is quick. About 1-2 days quick. And about $15 exactly.</li>\n  <li>Standard International: It’s $25, we can’t afford free yet. And takes around 7 - 14 working days.</li>\n  <li>(All timelines are subject to world pandemics) </li>\n</ul>"}],"upsells":[{"category":"Skincare","handles":["face-oil-1","face-oil-2","face-oil-3","cleanser"],"heading":"Shop Skincare","type":"Product"}],"sections":[{"type":"swipeImage","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.471264367816092,"src":"/static/726ee62ace9e63e02004fb2585f6967e/26852/pdp-face-oil-3-refill-how-to.jpg","srcSet":"/static/726ee62ace9e63e02004fb2585f6967e/d64b1/pdp-face-oil-3-refill-how-to.jpg 256w,\n/static/726ee62ace9e63e02004fb2585f6967e/89b9c/pdp-face-oil-3-refill-how-to.jpg 512w,\n/s