 recyclable with Soft Plastics through REDcycle once thoroughly cleaned.</li>\n  <li>We are working on Stage 2 of our refill model, which includes working on a solution that uses Sugarcane instead of plastic, however there exists no current option (that we have found) with a spout.</li>\n  <li>Would putting our refills in a large glass or aluminium bottle defeat the purpose of a refill? Would it become too expensive? More than the product itself?</li>\n  <li>This is our first step to reducing the amount of single use primary bottles, in a long journey.</li>\n</ul>"},{"key":"100% Vegan","heading":"100% Vegan and Cruelty Free","subheading":"Products that are good for your skin, your thoughts, and the planet.","content":"<ul>\n  <li>100% Australian Certified Organic Rose Otto Organic Floral Water (Rosa x Damascena).</li>\n  <li>Pure Rose Water works to refine open pores, minimise oiliness, and promote an awake, cool, fresh feeling.</li>\n  <li>This variety of Organic Rose Otto Floral Water has a somewhat different scent to other perceived Rose Floral Waters, it is highly concentrated in aroma and contains no preservatives. As part of the end products of distillation, the water has been saturated with essential oil during the distillation process and is given the names Floral Waters or Waters of Distillation.</li>\n</ul>"},{"key":"42 Day Returns","heading":"42 Day Return","subheading":"Our 42 Day Return Policy","content":"<ul>\n  <li>You can return your item within 42 days of receiving it, after chatting with our team, for a full refund or an exchange</li>\n  <li>We do this because we believe in and stand by our product, and you’ll have to have a pretty good reason for wanting to return it, and we’d like to honour that.</li>\n  <li>Why 42 days? Why not? Email <a href=\"mailto:bunnies@itsallfluff.com\" class=\"underline\">bunnies@itsallfluff.com</a> to tell us how you feel.</li>\n  <li>Be gentle, Fluff has feelings too.</li>\n</ul>"},{"key":"Free shipping over $50","heading":"Free Shipping","subheading":"Free Shipping over $50 in Aus","content":"<ul>\n  <li>Fluff ships products every Wednesday & Friday.</li>\n  <li>Free shipping for orders over $50 AUD </li>\n  <li>Otherwise it's $10 AUD. Delivered by Australia Post in about about a week.</li>\n  <li>Express Shipping: It’s not free, but it is quick. About 1-2 days quick. And about $15 exactly.</li>\n  <li>Standard International: It’s $25, we can’t afford free yet. And takes around 7 - 14 working days.</li>\n  <li>(All timelines are subject to world pandemics) </li>\n</ul>"}],"upsells":[{"category":"All","handles":["face-oil-1","face-oil-2","bronzing-powder-refill","lip-oil-refill"],"heading":"Best Sellers","type":"Product"}],"sections":[{"type":"swipeImage","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.471264367816092,"src":"/static/89e0001ffb722b3348ff4ad6394cd263/26852/pdp-floral-water-how-to.jpg","srcSet":"/static/89e0001ffb722b3348ff4ad6394cd263/d64b1/pdp-floral-water-how-to.jpg 256w,\n/static/89e0001ffb722b3348ff4ad6394cd263/89b9c/pdp-floral-water-how-to.jpg 512w,\n/static/89e0001ffb722b3348ff4ad6394cd263/26852/pdp-floral-water-how-to.jpg 1024w,\n/static/89e0001ffb722b3348ff4ad6394cd263/4d6da/pdp-floral-water-how-to.jpg 1344w","srcWebp":"/static/89e0001ffb722b3348ff4ad6394cd263/e0f73/pdp-floral-water-how-to.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/89e0001ffb722b3348ff4ad6394cd263/b42dd/pdp-floral-water-how-to.webp 256w,\n/static/89e0001ffb722b3348ff4ad6394cd263/e4e36/pdp-floral-water-how-to.webp 512w,\n/static/89e0001ffb722b3348ff4ad6394cd263/e0f73/pdp-floral-water-how-to.webp 1024w,\n/static/89e0001ffb722b3348ff4ad6394cd263/9b8f4/pdp-floral-water-how-to.webp 1344w","sizes":"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"}},"publicURL":"/static/89e0001ffb722b3348ff4ad6394cd263/pdp-floral-water-how-to.jpg"},"heading":"How to use","text":"Mist 1-2 pumps as desired, over face before or after makeup to add a dewy finish, through the hair to hydrate dry ends or to refresh skin throughout the day."},{