","heading":"100% Vegan and Cruelty Free","subheading":"Products that are good for your skin, your thoughts, and the planet.","content":"<ul>\n  <li>Sweet Almond Oil reduces puffiness while improving complexion and the appearance of scars.</li>\n  <li>Sunflower Seed Oil has rich antioxidant and anti-inflammatory properties hat soothe sensitive skin and redness.</li>\n  <li>Argan Kernal Oil - A natural sun protectant that moisturises and relieves skin from irritations and infections.</li>\n  <li>Jojoba Seed Oil - Containing essential fatty acids Omega 6 and 9, as well as Docosanol, which are antiviral and work to repair damaged skin cells.</li>\n  <li>Aloe Vera Leaf Extract - Containing anti-inflammatory antioxidants, enzymes, and Vitamins A and C.</li>\n  <li>Full Ingredient List - Ricinus communis (Castor) seed oil, Prunus amygdalus dulcis (Sweet almond) oil, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Butyrospermum parkii (Shea) butter, Euphorbia cerifera (Candelillia) wax, Mica (Sustainably Sourced), Copernicia cerifera (Carnauba) wax, Argania Spinosa (Argan) kernal oil, Simmondsia chinensis (Jojoba) seed oil, Squalane (Olive Oil) Glycine soja (Soybean) oil, Tocopherol Acetate (Vitamin E), Aloe barbadensis (Aloe Vera) leaf extract, Citric Acid, CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide) CI 77491, 77492, 77499 (Iron Oxides)</li>\n</ul>"},{"key":"42 Day Returns","heading":"42 Day Return","subheading":"Our 42 Day Return Policy","content":"<ul>\n  <li>You can return your item within 42 days of receiving it, after chatting with our team, for a full refund or an exchange</li>\n  <li>We do this because we believe in and stand by our product, and you’ll have to have a pretty good reason for wanting to return it, and we’d like to honour that.</li>\n  <li>Why 42 days? Why not? Email <a href=\"mailto:bunnies@itsallfluff.com\" class=\"underline\">bunnies@itsallfluff.com</a> to tell us how you feel.</li>\n  <li>Be gentle, Fluff has feelings too.</li>\n</ul>"},{"key":"Free shipping over $50","he